Life is complex;
Life is a mystery i don't understand
some people are playing, some working, others are just relaxing;
Some live under bridges, some have several mansions;
Some can eat comfortably, some do not have food, and others look up to God for daily bread.
What an  unfair and unequal  life
http://fastgodstuff.com/files/2011/10/why_is_life_unfair_top-400x2151.jpg

I have travelled overlands and overseas 
I have different faces, color, and tongues
Yet humans meet the same different fate when it comes to life;
Some people work hard, yet they make a little for a living
Others work a little and make wealth;
What an unfair and unequal life
http://img00.deviantart.net/0981/i/2009/257/7/5/life_is_unfair_by_mido_lb.jpg

The rich worry about keeping his wealth,
The poor worry about making wealth;
Those at the top of the ladder will never pull those below the ladder down,
Those down the ladder will never push someone up;
ohh what an unfair and unequal life
htt

WHEN  I HAD NO MONEY, AND I WAS LIVING FROM HAND TO MOUTH
YOU WERE ALWAYS THERE;

WHEN I HAD NO HOUSE, AND I STAY ALL NIGHT TRYING TO SURVIVE THE COLD BREEZE;
YOU WERE ALWAYS THERE;

WHEN I HAD JUST A PAIR OF TROUSER, A SHIRT, AND NO SHOE TO KEEP MY FEET WARM;
YOU WERE ALWAYS THERE;

EVEN WHEN FRIENDS AND FAMILY TOLD YOU DIFFERENT THINGS TO MAKE ABSTAIN FROM ME;
YOU WERE ALWAYS THERE;

I LEFT YOU AND TRAVELED EAST TO SURVIVE AND MAKE A LIVING, 10 YEARS PAST, AND WHEN I ARRIVED;
YOU WERE STILL THERE

NOW I OWN SEVERAL HERDS, AND RIDE ON ANY HORSE I WISH TO ANYWHERE I WANT.
AND I ASKED YOU; HUMAN WHY HAVE YOU ALWAYS BEEN THERE FOR ME?
BUT YOU SAID JUST ONE THING

**TRUE LOVE**
